572
00:37:38,740 --> 00:37:42,530
Also, Mo Fei, aren't you the one who instigated all this behind the scenes?

573
00:37:42,530 --> 00:37:46,100
If you hadn't told her that I took Cheng Yang back, would I have got slapped?

574
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:49,200
Now you come to me and pretend to be the good person?

575
00:37:49,200 --> 00:37:50,880
Forget it.

576
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,760
You disgust me.

577
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,640
Jiaxi.

578
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:57,200
You are my friend. How could I do that to you?

579
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:59,280
Please believe me.

