00:38:00,080 --> 00:38:02,320
Believe you?

581
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:05,760
Do you finally know what it's like for others to not believe you?

582
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:09,830
What you are going through right now is less than half of what I have been through.

583
00:38:09,830 --> 00:38:13,330
Do you want me to forgive you? Fine.

